<!-- 4.6.15 -->
<div class='toload theorem'>
	<p><span class='envidentifier'>Theorem 4.6.15</span>
	$S$ is $E$-unitary if and only if it admits a topologically free partial action satisfying (i) and (ii) of Proposition <span class='ref' data-tag='propositionconditionsonpartialactionthatimplyeunitary'></span>.
	</p>
</div>